  "title": "‽Silly Poems for Awesome Adults‽",
  "description": "There is much that is funny / about a duck-billed platypus / but when they see a human / do they also laugh at us? | Adults deserve whimsy too! With poetry, interrobangs, and neurodivergence, Wade delights in exploring absurdity and making meaning in life. (Prev. Fringe: Charade, Most Honest Man. Jubilations: Howard in Big Bang)",
